      "created": 1772311770,
      "updated": 1772311770
    },
    {
      "id": "69a354d90000000000a6b7f6",
      "text": "\t[CosenseのSmart Contextが外部URL生成に対応してる]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772311770,
      "updated": 1772318888
    },
    {
      "id": "69a320c37838e30000004bce68",
      "text": "\t今週花粉のせいで運動してないので、いいかげんやる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772298434,
      "updated": 1772314433
    },
    {
      "id": "69a35f130000000000700916",
      "text": "\t\tやっぱ俺って外向的なのかもしれないな、引きこもるの難しい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772314387,
      "updated": 1772314401
    },
    {
      "id": "69a35f220000000000700917",
      "text": "\t\t今週は致命的な事態は防げてる、さて薬の効果がどこまで続くか、外練に耐えられるのか……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772314402,
      "updated": 1772314425
    },
    {
      "id": "69a35f3c0000000000700918",
      "text": "\t\tdone 07:39:40、さて……",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772314428,
      "updated": 1772318382
    },
    {
      "id": "69a37e7000000000001999a5",
      "text": "\t\t\t喉がイガイガする 08:46:59",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772322416,
      "updated": 1772322420
    },
    {
      "id": "69a37e6b00000000001999a4",
      "text": "\t\t動画はできた: [OKP Cipher サビ地帯解説 #DDS #DanceDanceShuffle - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/shorts/DwToZBBxKJw]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772322412,
      "updated": 1772322415
    },
    {
      "id": "69a35f060000000000700915",
      "text": "\tよく噛まない・噛めない人は喉越しを重視してる説？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772314374,
      "updated": 1772318614
    },
    {
      "id": "69a36f960000000000c4d347",
      "text": "\t\tよく噛むと喉越しも何もない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318614,
      "updated": 1772318623
    },
    {
      "id": "69a36fa30000000000c4d348",
      "text": "\t\t逆にあまり噛まないと原形留めてるので喉越しがある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318628,
      "updated": 1772318638
    },
    {
      "id": "69a36fae0000000000c4d349",
      "text": "\t\t\tここに快感？を抱いているのではないか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318639,
      "updated": 1772318644
    },
    {
      "id": "69a36fb40000000000c4d34a",
      "text": "\t\tと思ったのは、ミスってあまり噛まずに飲み込んだときに「おわっ、喉の触感すごいな」「……これ気持ちよくね？」と少し思ったから",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318644,
      "updated": 1772318786
    },
    {
      "id": "69a370230000000000c4d34c",
      "text": "\t\t\tいわゆる[喉越し]という概念はこれなのでは？と思ったから",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318756,
      "updated": 1772318768
    },
    {
      "id": "69a36ff60000000000c4d34b",
      "text": "\t\t別軸:",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318710,
      "updated": 1772318796
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3704c0000000000c4d34d",
      "text": "\t\t\t飲み物は炭酸やビールが有名",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772318796,
      "updated": 1772318810
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3704c0000000000c4d34e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[喉がイガイガ]するときに飲食物流し込むと少し気持ちいい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772318797,
      "updated": 1772333019
    },
    {
      "id": "69a37d850000000000f9e69d",
      "text": "\t今日はこれを見る",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772322181,
      "updated": 1772323480
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3829700000000009f83bd",
      "text": "\t\t[KING of Performai The 7th 全国決勝大会【生配信】 - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZT7p-vEkXWY]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772323480,
      "updated": 1772323480
    },
    {
      "id": "69a382ac00000000009f83be",
      "text": "\t\tmaimaiはよしきだろうなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772323500,
      "updated": 1772323506
    },
    {
      "id": "69a382b100000000009f83bf",
      "text": "\t\t\t[【maimai CiRCLE】 裏皆伝 合格!!!!! - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=23YqJ5Scln8]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772323506,
      "updated": 1772323506
    },
    {
      "id": "69a382b100000000009f83c0",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれ誰が勝てるん",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772323506,
      "updated": 1772323510
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3a15f00000000004af428",
      "text": "\t\t[からめる]さんも出てる（恒例）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772331360,
      "updated": 1772335690
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3f567000000000065a1cd",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/bfae4e9c4bb64964548c67796cfc8163]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772352873,
      "updated": 1772352874
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1ec000000000089463b",
      "text": "\t\t筐体メンテ悪くね？クレームで盛り上がってチェック入ってる展開 12:26:51",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772335598,
